photoswipe markup
Root element of PhotoSwipe. Must have class pswp.
Background of PhotoSwipe. 
         It's a separate element as animating opacity is faster than rgba().
Slides wrapper with overflow:hidden.
Container that holds slides. 
            PhotoSwipe keeps only 3 of them in the DOM to save memory.
            Don't modify these 3 pswp__item elements, data is added later on.
Default (PhotoSwipeUI_Default) interface on top of sliding area. Can be changed.
Controls are self-explanatory. Order can be changed.

Las Olas Beach Club of Satellite Beach
Our oceanfront resort provides spacious accommodations, a convenient location, and a tropical setting. Enjoy your own private balcony with a breathtaking view of the ocean.
Book Now
Resort Highlights
Beach Access
Your vacation condo is just steps from the ocean via our private beach access.
Amenities
Our heated pool and hot tub are open every day of the year.
Full Kitchens
All units have a full-size kitchen with any dishes, utilities, and cookware you may need.
Free WiFi
Free and unlimited WiFi is available throughout the resort.
Gallery
Main Bedroom
The main bedroom has a king bed, TV, and en-suite bathroom. Some units have balcony access from the bedroom.
Button
Year-Round Pool & Hot Tub
The pool deck is open every day of the year, and the pool is heated during the colder months.
Button
Living/Dining Area
Our 1400+ sq ft units provide plenty of space for you and your guests.
Button
Main Bathroom
Both the en-suite and guest bathrooms were recently renovated with vinyl floors and lighted mirrors.
Button
Breathtaking Views
Watch the sunrise from your oceanfront condo.
Button
Full Kitchen
Full size refrigerator, range, microwave, and dishwasher in every unit. In-unit laundry too!
Living Room
The sofa contains a queen bed - each unit sleeps up to 6 people.
Button
Guest Bedroom
All units are 2-bed/2-bath, so there's room for the whole family!
Button
Private Beach Access
You're only a few steps from the sand with our gated beach access.
Button

Las Olas Beach Club of Cocoa Beach
We look forward to welcoming you to our beautiful resort in Cocoa Beach, where you’ll enjoy spacious accommodations that are maintained with pride. Conveniently located near famous destinations like Ron Jon Surf Shop and the Cocoa Beach Pier.
Book Now
Resort Highlights
Beach Access
Your vacation condo is just steps from the ocean via our private beach access.
Amenities
Our heated pool and hot tub are open every day of the year.
Full Kitchens
All units have a full-size kitchen with any dishes, utilities, and cookware you may need.
Free WiFi
Free and unlimited WiFi is available throughout the resort.
Gallery
Main Bedroom
The main bedroom has a king bed, TV, Roman soaking tub, and en-suite bathroom. Some units may have a view of the ocean.
Button
Full Kitchen
Full size refrigerator, range, microwave, and dishwasher in every unit. In-unit laundry too!
Button
Living Area
Our units provide plenty of space for you and your guests.
